mering Europe and United States of the Roaring Twenties.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCulture conflictvFiction. 0aNineteen twentiesvFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aFagan, Teresa Lavender.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311063898140uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030023157140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300231571423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300231571/original  a978-3-11-063898-1  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles